**Critical Optimizations:**
1. **Parallelism:** Use all 64 cores with morsel-driven execution (10K–100K rows/thread)
2. **Zone-Maps:** Build on date columns (l_shipdate, o_orderdate) for 85%+ block skips
3. **Filter Selectivity:** Aggressive pushdown of highly selective predicates (0.004–0.17)
4. **Join Strategy:** Hash joins dominate; partial aggregation reduces intermediates
5. **Subquery Decorrelation:** Convert correlated subqueries in Q9, Q17, Q20, Q22 to CTEs/semi-joins

**Bottleneck Queries:** Q3 (shipping priority), Q5 (supplier volume), Q7 (volume shipping), Q9 (profit), Q18 (large volume customer) — all involve 3–6 table joins + aggregation.

